high_descs: Move to the microwave.
Pick up the spoon next to the microwave.
Bring the spoon to the fridge.
Put the spoon in the bowl in the fridge.
Pick up the bowl from the fridge.
Bring the bowl to the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around then turn right to face the microwave.
Pick up the spoon that is on the counter.
Turn around then head to the opposite side of the room in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the spoon inside the bowl.
Grab the bowl and close the fridge.
Turn left and head back to the sink.
Place the bowl into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the bowl with the spoon in it into the sink.

high_descs: Turn and go to the coffee maker
Grab the metal spoon next to the coffee maker.
Turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge. Set the spoon on plate on the second shelf.
Grab the plate with the spoon that is on the second shelf.
Turn and go to the sink.
Set the plate with the spoon in to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put plate with spoon in the sink.
